quizzes.question:
Type in a code to declare variable b and assign a's value to b, and then print their sum to the screen.
[!raw!]
int a = 15;
int b = {0};
cout << a {1} b << endl;

quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Variables[/h1]

A variable's value may be changed as many times as necessary throughout the program.

[b]For example:[/b] [code format="cpp" codeId="181"]int a = 100;
[b]a = 50;[/b]
cout << a;

// Outputs [b]50[/b][/code]
